job.title: ISI Kolkata Notification 2021 – Opening for Various Executive Posts
job.body:
Total Vacancies: Various

Name of the post:

  • Project Manager

Description:

The Indian Statistical Institute, Kolkata issued a total of various vacancies for the posts of Project Manager The online application for these posts under ISI shall start from 01.04.2021. The eligible and interested candidates can apply for this online application before 15.04.2021. For further detailed information regarding educational qualifications, age limit, selection procedure, how to apply, etc. for these posts is mentioned below. For more such updates do visit theprograd.com .The ProGrad jobs.

 

Mode of application & application fee:

The application fee for ISI Kolkata Notification 2021:

  • Mode of application: Online
  • For more details, you can refer to the notification. The link is given at the bottom.

Important dates:

  • The Starting date to apply online is 01.04.2021.
  • The Last date to apply online is 15.04.2021

Educational qualification:

  • You must have the B.E./B. Tech, M.E./M. Tech from a recognized university to apply for the post of Project Manager

Age limit criteria:

  • The minimum age required to apply is: 21 years
  • The maximum age required to apply is: 45 years

For age relaxation criteria, you can refer to the notification. The link is given below in The ProGrad jobs.

Pay Scale:

  • The pay scale as per 7th pay commission for the post of Project Manager is: 60000-80000 per month
  • Check the detailed notification also something has missed. 

How to apply for ISI Kolkata Notification 2021?

  • First, visit the official website.
  • Register yourself on the portal of ISI.
  • Login yourself on the portal.
  • Find the notification of the Project Manager
  • Fill up the complete details that are asked in the application form.
  • Upload your photo and signature with the dimensions asked in the instructions.
  • Submit the application fee
  • Finally, download the application form for future needs.
